CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 23, 1961, pg. 32 reads: "Dimperio and Backs - Coach Pete Dimperio (extreme right) is seen instructing four of his backs, as the Westinghouse High "Bulldogs" prepared to meet tough North Catholic High over the week-end. Left to right: Jon Henderson, John Brewer Jr., Melvin Myricks and (standing) George Webb.  White thugs slugged Henderson, last week, shortly after Homewooders defeated Mt. Lebanon, 12-6. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Westinghouse High School football coach Pete Dimperio talking to football players from left: Jon Henderson, John Brewer Jr., Melvin Myricks, and George Webb standing in back
